Module org.nasdanika.engineering
Package org.nasdanika.engineering

Interface Activity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, ConnectionSource, ConnectionTarget, EngineeredElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Forum, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, ModelElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, NamedElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Operation, org.nasdanika.ncore.Period
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivityImpl
    public interface Activity
extends Operation
    A representation of the model object 'Activity'. Activity is an operation which can pass control to another activity.

    The following features are supported:

    • Outbound Transitions
    • Inbound Transitions
    See Also:
